{"tid":1048951,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"教畜入一入黎","createTime":"2019-03-06T02:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T05:38:47.000Z","uid":197216,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d78935fd2faa44e68923533cf8021e7368b17ccb","tid":1048951,"uid":197216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:58:30.000Z","msg":"我女朋友係小學英文老師 有教埋Art<br />\n舊年十二月先開始一齊<br />\n一對剛剛開始拍拖既情侶 應該好甜蜜<br />\n但我呢個女朋友 <br />\n星期六日一係就話要番工 <br />\n一係就話要係屋企出卷改文<br />\n<br />\n好啦 下個月有個長假復活節 打算同佢放鬆下去旅行<br />\n但又話咩校長唔喜歡 老師去旅行 會比說話佢地聽<br />\n例如 去完旅行就會話你 教學表現差左 改簿馬虎左<br />\n所以佢都唔敢再去旅行<br />\n<br />\n我想問 咁多位教畜，現實係咪會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924ff2b2fed88d02511b9e65de2920263ffed43b","tid":1048951,"uid":45095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"帽事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee7346e87c5f85aaaedab84cfffce58df110e0b","tid":1048951,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:59:58.000Z","msg":"佢鍾意做教師多過鍾意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3647dea2e473b1418390f7bf7c818a14cc3cce60","tid":1048951,"uid":142878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:00:14.000Z","msg":"甚至鍾意咗校長"},{"pid":"1f70e754fd285302b1ecca19377704825cdccbba","tid":1048951,"uid":45095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:02:11.000Z","msg":"佢教左幾多年先？"},{"pid":"9e3b181fd7abdd14fd9eb69318479f445f6f4565","tid":1048951,"uid":8276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:03:48.000Z","msg":"第一段正常<br />\n因為份工真係會侵蝕埋私人時間<br />\n尤其新入行 又未慣 未拿捏到<br />\n又會俾人塞野俾你做<br />\n<br />\n但第二段就學校問題<br />\n咩唔鍾意老師去旅行<br />\n我就唔信間學校d老一輩冇去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你壯下你女朋友個膽啦"},{"pid":"3494b5198cfddea84bb6ea72db5da2430d8b385c","tid":1048951,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"